\bMidna Town is connected to both Suntouched City and Narra Town.\nTo get to Suntouched, you just leave to the west...

\rDid you know? Electrode is the third fastest non-mega and non-legendary Pokemon!

\bThey say he rode upon Arceus itself!
\bI hope they take this statue down.
\bIt's so disgusting what he did to the entire region. I hope he falls in a fire.
\bThere's a lot of cool new Mega Evolutions that have only been seen in the Torren Region.
\bTyphlosion, Eevee, Marowak... agh! I want to see them all!
\bI'm a trainer with a great track record!\nI've won one out of every ten games- but I swear the ones I lost were only because my opponents cheated!
\bI heard Orion, the leader of Suntouched City, is a total weirdo.\nHe talks to rocks and still has an imaginary friend!
\rI'm going to win the next Trainer School tournament, I just know it!

\bMy taxi, for the low cost of $500, will get you wherever you need to go!
\b... ... as long as you've been there before, that is.
\bCome back with $500 and I'll show you what I mean!
\bI jumped down those ledges over there thinking there'd be a way for me to get back up.
\bApparently the only way for me to get back to Narra Town quickly is to climb those rocks!
\bI should calm down.\nStaying mad about this isn't going to help me out of this situation.
\bHere, take this and put it to good use.
\bOkay, I guess I should start making the long trek back to Narra Town.
\bWho knows, maybe the journey will make my team and I stronger?
Ringing it now would probably lead a horde of angry students up here...
